ph has no consecutive-no-op detection. The circuit breaker shows all zeros at loop 17 — it does not count no-op sessions as \"no progress.\" Ralph checks `stories_remaining > 0` without filtering flagged stories.\n- **Wasted session ratio: 68.4%** (13/19 sessions today produced nothing).\n- **Three P0 action items** must be resolved before starting another ralph run:\n  1. Add consecutive-no-op termination (3+ no-ops = exit)\n  2. Fix circuit breaker to count no-ops\n  3. Do not start ralph again until those two are done"}],"totalDurationMs":95045,"totalTokens":30564,"totalToolUseCount":13,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2750,"cache_read_input_tokens":27541,"output_tokens":272,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2750},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
